timing_socv_rc_variation_mode(25.10)      timing_socv_rc_variation_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_socv_rc_variation_mode

Syntax
       timing_socv_rc_variation_mode

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables modeling of interconnect variation in SOCV mode.

       The SOCV flow provides support for RC variation on the interconnect.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

